title: Flight.Simulator.X-TeamToyota
description:
The Sky is Boundless, the World is Alive
IMMERSE yourself in this dynamic, living world of fun. Challenge yourself by flying any of 50+ missions all over the world. Whether its your first time on the tarmac, or you're a Flight Simulator veteran, get set for adventure on a global scale.


Minimum System Requirements - 

1.0 GHz Processor or higher
256mb RAM on Windows XP 
512mb RAM on Windows Vista
15 GB Free Hard Drive Space
DirectX 9.0c Compliant Video Card with 32mb of RAM and support for hardware transformation and lighting
56.6kbps or better internet connection for online play

Deluxe edition includes - 

-More high-detail cities and airports in some of the most spectacular places
-Structured missions to test your skills
-Enhanced multiplayer features like shared aircraft and live tower control
-More airplanes including the Maule M7-260C Super Rocket w/ Wheels & Skis
-Introducing the Garmin1000 glass cockpit
